#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"A variety of pencils and pens provided for writing assignments, note-taking,"
" and completing tests and quizzes."
msgstr ""
"ສໍ ແລະ ບິກຫຼາກຫຼາຍຊະນິດທີ່ຈັດກຽມໄວ້ສຳລັບການຂຽນບົດຝຶກຫັດ, ການຈົດບັນທຶກ, ແລະ ການເຮັດບົດສອບເສັງ."

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_key_images
msgid "A vibrant community of thinkers and innovators"
msgstr "ສັງຄົມແຫ່ງການຮຽນຮູ້ທີ່ເຕັມໄປດ້ວຍນັກຄິດ ແລະ ນັກສ້າງສັນ"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_quadrant
msgid "Academic Excellence"
msgstr "ຄວາມເປັນເລີດທາງດ້ານວິຊາການ"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_empowerment
msgid "Achieve with<br/>Summit University"
msgstr "ປະສົບຄວາມສຳເລັດໄປກັບ<br/>ມະຫາວິທະຍາໄລ Summit"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_cards_grid
msgid "Advanced Learning Programs"
msgstr "ຫຼັກສູດການຮຽນຮູ້ຂັ້ນສູງ"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Advanced scientific calculators for math and science courses, helping "
"students perform complex calculations with ease."
msgstr ""
"ຈັກຄິດໄລ່ທາງວິທະຍາສາດຂັ້ນສູງສຳລັບວິຊາຄະນິດສາດ ແລະ ວິທະຍາສາດ, ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ນັກສຶກສາສາມາດຄິດໄລ່ເລກທີ່ຊັບຊ້"
"ອນໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ."

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_company_team_detail
msgid ""
"Alexander Rivera is an economics professor focused on macroeconomic theory "
"and international finance."
msgstr ""
"Alexander Rivera ແມ່ນອາຈານສອນດ້ານເສດຖະສາດ ທີ່ເນັ້ນໃສ່ທິດສະດີເສດຖະສາດມະຫາພາກ ແລະ ການເງິນ"
"ລະຫວ່າງປະເທດ."

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_image_text
msgid "All students benefit from individualised support."
msgstr "ນັກສຶກສາທຸກຄົນໄດ້ຮັບຜົນປະໂຫຍດຈາກການສະໜັບສະໜູນແບບສ່ວນຕົວ."

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_cover
msgid "Always at the top"
msgstr "ຢູ່ອັນດັບຕົ້ນໆສະເໝີ"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid "Art Supplies Kit"
msgstr "ຊຸດອຸປະກອນສິລະປະ"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_cards_grid
msgid ""
"Benefit from tailored academic advising and support services, designed to "
"guide you through your educational journey."
msgstr ""
"ໄດ້ຮັບຜົນປະໂຫຍດຈາກການໃຫ້ຄຳປຶກສາທາງດ້ານວິຊາການ ແລະ ການບໍລິການສະໜັບສະໜູນທີ່ຖືກອອກແບບມາເພື່ອແນະນ"
"ຳທ່ານຕະຫຼອດການຮຽນ."

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_key_images
msgid "Building the leaders of tomorrow"
msgstr "ສ້າງຜູ້ນຳແຫ່ງມື້ອື່ນ"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_company_team_detail
msgid "Chemistry Professor"
msgstr "ອາຈານສອນວິຊາເຄມີສາດ"

#. module: theme_bewise
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_bewise.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Complete set of art supplies including colored pencils, markers, paints, and"
